column2: SELECT TOP # e.SystemStudentID as StudentID, e.GradeLevel as EnrollmentGrade, e.SchoolYear4Digit as SchoolYear4Digit, t.TestPeriod as Period, t.TestSubjectGroup as AssessmentSubject, e.SystemStudentID as MetricSource, t.TestType as MetricName, t.TestScore as Score, t.TestDate as IsMostRecent FROM Enrollment as e JOIN TestScores as t ON e.SystemStudentID = t.SystemStudentID JOIN ParentEngagement as p ON e.SystemStudentID = p.SystemStudentID
